<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">2024年7月1日是中国共产党成立103周年，当天，我校在创客中心举行“庆祝中国共产党成立103周年暨‘七一’ 总结表彰大会”顺利举行 。</span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2016%3A34%3A41189ad77a257a1f17ec8b54d2cb6e9cf.png?Expires=2035269282&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=diy9Vk%2Fom%2BDJTRUm3I%2FdGfgpv9c%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2016%3A34%3A41189ad77a257a1f17ec8b54d2cb6e9cf.png?Expires=2035269282&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=diy9Vk%2Fom%2BDJTRUm3I%2FdGfgpv9c%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></a></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">大会在庄严的国歌声和重温入党誓词中拉开帷幕。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">校党委书记、督导专员江延湖同志向广大师生党员致以节日的问候，向受表彰的先进单位和优秀个人表示热烈祝贺；总结了学校一年来始终坚持党建引领“走在前”、始终坚持立德树人“勇争先”、始终坚持实干担当“善作为”等方面取得的成效。他提出三点意见：<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">一是在初心使命中汲取奋进力量，</strong>要进一步增强责任意识和担当精神，要进一步汇聚起强大的发展力量；<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">二是在学纪知纪明纪守纪中筑牢堤坝，</strong>全校师生党员要争做表率，敢担当、善作为，各级党组织要做到暑假期间“工作不断档、标准不放松”，始终坚持两手抓两促进，把开展党纪学习教育同学校重点工作推进相结合，确保取得实效；<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">三是要立足本职岗位勇于担当作为，</strong>以“时时放心不下 、事事心里有底、件件落实到位”的责任感和紧迫感，进一步提升作风能力。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2016%3A28%3A32f3913274c19aa5c27edd027d3b97999.jpg?Expires=2035268912&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ZDp4E%2FR3RBS3xvujoFBQUXZnBtw%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2016%3A28%3A32f3913274c19aa5c27edd027d3b97999.jpg?Expires=2035268912&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=ZDp4E%2FR3RBS3xvujoFBQUXZnBtw%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/>&nbsp;</a>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">校党委副书记、执行校长范红铭同志在主持时，提出了要求：<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">一是</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">要高度重视</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">、</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">认真传达并贯彻落实本次会议精神</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">，</strong>各单位须深刻把握会议精神实质，结合自身实际情况将会议精神传达下去；<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">二是</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">要认真履职，深入推进全面从严治党向基层延伸</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">，</strong>各单位须有效部署“大抓落实年”重要活动和学校党建工作重点任务；<strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">三是要</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">全员联动，全力抓好各项工作的落实</strong><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;">，</strong>各单位须创新方式方法，凝聚全员智慧与力量，促进学校各项工作高质量发展。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2016%3A29%3A50b1007bc4c9c7b784818503ebcb54ca7.jpg?Expires=2035268991&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=%2B0h65GyoHwG3%2B00Duv%2BIJPAlWNg%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2016%3A29%3A50b1007bc4c9c7b784818503ebcb54ca7.jpg?Expires=2035268991&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=%2B0h65GyoHwG3%2B00Duv%2BIJPAlWNg%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/>&nbsp;</a>&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">校党委副书记高建国同志宣读《关于表彰2023-2024年度先进基层党组织、优秀共产党员和优秀党务工作者的决定》，与会领导向受表彰的先进单位和优秀个人颁奖。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">&nbsp;<a href="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2016%3A29%3A109098ca14ada42f6bff750a8b8ceebc7.jpg?Expires=2035268951&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=CF31YrmXnGqlVgJ2897tjCnnmD4%3D" data-fancybox="gallery" style="box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 122, 183); text-decoration-line: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; transition: all 0.3s ease-in 0s;">&nbsp;<img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/jiiewebsite/img/2024-07-02%2016%3A29%3A109098ca14ada42f6bff750a8b8ceebc7.jpg?Expires=2035268951&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=CF31YrmXnGqlVgJ2897tjCnnmD4%3D" class="imgstyle" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); width: 600px; height: 400px;" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></a></span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;">先进基层党组织代表曾继勇同志、优秀共产党员代表蔡瑜萍同志、优秀党务工作者代表曾丽文同志依次作典型交流发言。</span></p><p style="text-align:justify;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 1px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 2; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; list-style-type: none; vertic